{
  "stem": "2568.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she had one adopted daughter, married with a child, and her oldest daughter with a child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were like 15 people in two rooms-- one room with a little kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the ghetto, she had a much, little bigger apartment, but it was still [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wires.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We could go out and come wherever we wanted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a Jewish police too, which they were watching.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But before the ghetto, even we used to live during the Germans, we had two-- twice, they made like a pogroms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you know what's a pogrom?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to take people and kill them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It became less.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not so easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow we managed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people didn't have-- they were hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were dying in the streets, swollen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Typhus-- a lot of people were sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was one of the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't get the typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was not easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had-- my mother left was everything hidden under the ground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one day we were sitting in a bunker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My cousins were very handy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And under the cellar, we had bunkers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the ghetto and in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This happened in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were sitting under the cellar, there was like a little-- not a cellar, but [? water full. ?] So my sister was ready to get married before they killed her.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the whole fiance, he knew everything that my mother had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he took me one evening out from the-- that basement, and he showed me where everything lays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he even helped me to dig out everything from under the ground.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
